# Per-milestone Phase 1 STOP working files + recovery files (D-F4 / D-GITIGNORE).
# Format: .{milestone}-phase1-stop.md / .{milestone}-recovery.md.
# Authored during the milestone-1 STOP discipline, removed before commit.
.m*-phase1-stop.md
.m*-recovery.md

# M5 design archive — scratch / iteration / ui_kits exports kept
# locally for reference but not load-bearing for the chat shell.
# The handoff/, brand/, assets/, fonts/, screenshots/, and root
# CSS files in design/m5-handoff/ ARE tracked.
design/m5-handoff/uploads/
design/m5-handoff/scratch/
design/m5-handoff/ui_kits/
